Dialogs.Dialog: Well, I'm okay with social sciences but I'm very bad at math...
Lately, I didn't do well with my study... How about you...？
Hey, there are materials that I don't quite get in class. I wonder if you're free after school...
Then come to my house. I'll be waiting.
Then come to Rinko's house after school.
Then you can come to my house after school. I'll have to trouble you.
Eh？ You have something even more important than Rinko！？
Eh？ You still have time to have fun？ Exams are getting close.
It's almost time for exams to start, huh, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko was thinking about studying with you but you are having fun here.
Right, it's almost exam time again for us, huh, ▲小早川＊▲...
Eh？ What a coincidence. Well, do you have some free time after this？ There's something I don't get...
Right, it's almost exam time again for us, huh, ▲小早川＊▲...
Then come to my house after this.
I didn't ask for your help... but it's okay.
You're reliable. Then I'll be waiting at home.
Ah, is that so？ What a cold-hearted guy.
Really...？ Then maybe next time... Next time, okay？
I have something that I don't quite understand. How about we study together？
Then come to Rinko's house. You'll teach Rinko, too, right？ You're an upperclassman, after all.
I have something that I don't quite understand. How about we study together？
And you need help from an underclassman？ Well, that is fine. Come to Rinko's house then.
I have something that I don't quite understand. How about we study together？
Of course, that's okay. Come to Rinko's house, okay？
It's your first time to get in my room, right？ Welcome.
Okay, welcome. Let me tell you one thing. If you do anything weird, I'll get the security guard to arrest you.
Say... This is your first time to get in my room, right？
I already told the security guard that you're my boyfriend.
(Or they might think that I'm a suspicious person？)
Hey, you have come to Rinko's house quite often, huh？
You can look as much as you want, but you have to forget everything when you leave.
I don't have anything of value here.
I know it's my own room, but somehow, I'm getting nervous...
Hey, let's get ready for studying.
Hehe. I need to calm myself down a bit.
Hey, come on. Have a seat.
There will be 3 questions. If you answer them all correctly, you'll get a reward.
You really got them all correct... I promised you a reward, right...？
All correct, huh？ Then Rinko will give you a reward...
I can't give you a reward. This is regrettable.
Okay, too bad. You didn't get all the answers right. No reward.
This is regrettable, but I can't give you any reward.
It can't be helped. Let's try once more.
What do you wanna do？ I don't mind doing this again, though.
You're way too bad to get any reward.
Too bad... You missed too many of them.
Try to you get it right this time.
Geez... I have no choice. Just wait a moment.
Hey... Do you want to get closer to me...？
Something is quite lacking here, huh...？
You are not allowed to stare...
I went through the trouble for this... So it's your privilege to look at me...
Okay, the reward. Think of it as my debut.
Your reward. I think most guys like something like this, right？
Your reward. What do you think when you look at Rinko？
Okay, time's up for your reward.
This is it for the reward！ Argh！ It's embarrassing.
Okay. That's enough. We'll continue next time.
If you answer another set of questions correctly, I'll show you a different costume. How's that？
Okay. Then another round of challenge.
I see. Then we'll do this later.
Since you really tried your best, here's a special...
This is special... Do you feel motivated？
It can't be helped... Here. Will this motivate you a little bit？
Geez. If this can't really motivate you, I don't know what will.
It's embarrassing... I hope this helps motivate you.
What do you think about this？
Somehow... I can't feel at ease...
I feel like I'm punished to wear this.
How long are you going to look...？ Idiot...
Hey, I said there's nothing here...
Is this kind of outfit okay...？
You don't care much about my outfit, huh...？
Like this, do I look strange...？
Then this should be it for today.
Thank you. I think I've learned many things today.
Now I'm more confident. I'll probably get good grades on the exams.
Thank you for today. Like this, I'm sure I can do my best on the exams.
I still feel uneasy about the exams...
Well... I didn't feel much like we were reviewing lessons...
It didn't go well. What should I do...？
We didn't make that much progress on our lesson reviews...
It didn't go well... I feel like it was such a waste of time...
This is not good. Now, I feel very uneasy about the exams...
It's already this late. We should stop here.
It's this time already？ Do you have to hurry home？
I still want to be here
Okay. I'll see you off then...
Thanks for coming. I'll try my best with my study.
Somehow, it wasn't a good idea for you to come here. Our study didn't go well either...
The way we use to review our lessons was a bit weird...
